channel.title: My Electron - 13 [WIP]
channel.description:
Hey guys, I've been chewing on this one for a long time, and thought I'd post a version. I want to see if you have any ideas on how to flesh out a track like this. What does it need? I feel like it has a pretty solid hook in the middle, but it just isn't close to finished. Any advice would be so appreciated. Thanks!
